videos.description: Broderick Robinson grabs the rebound and pushes up the floor to nail a 3-pointer in transition..
videos.headline: Robinson's 3-pointer gives UMKC early lead

videos.description: Shaquille Morris hits a 3-pointer from the top of the arc to extend the lead for the Shockers.
videos.headline: Morris drains 3-pointer to extend Wichita State's lead

videos.description: Landry Shamet drives from half court for a two-hand slam for the Shockers.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_Final Game Highlight (Shamet drives and slams it home for Wichita State) 2017/11/10

videos.headline: Shamet drives and slams it home for Wichita State

videos.description: Samajae Haynes-Jones finds Shaquille Morris for an easy two-hand dunk for the Shockers late in the first half.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Haynes-Jones and Morris connect for dunk

videos.description: Landry Shamet nails a corner 3-pointer as the shot clock expires to extend the lead for the Shockers.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Shamet beats the shot clock

videos.description: Zach Brown blocks the layup attempt of UMKC's Xavier Bishop in transition.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Brown gets back for a nasty  block
